<title>Verify terminology</title>

<div class="main">
<h1>Terminology verification</h1>

<p>All parameters are mandatory. Make sure the language direction is the same
as in the bitext and glossary files</p>

<form method=post enctype=multipart/form-data>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Verification parameters:</legend>
  <input type="radio" name="directions" id="direction1" value="eng-rus"> English-Russian </input><br>
  <input type="radio" name="directions" id="direction2" value="rus-eng" required> Russian-English </input><br><br>

  <input type="radio" name="outcomes" id="outcome1" value="errors"> Get errors </input><br>
  <input type="radio" name="outcomes" id="outcome2" value="successes" required> Get successes </input><br><br>

  <label for=bitext>Bitext*: </label>
  <input type=file name=bitext required><br><br>

  <label for=glossary>Glossary**: </label>
  <input type=file name=glossary required><br><br>

  <input type=submit value=Verify class="button"/>

  </fieldset>
</form>

<p>*Bitext must be a tab-delimiated .txt file, one pair of sentences per line</p>

<p>**Glossary must be a tab-delimiated .txt file, one pair of terms per line</p>
